More About Me

Bio

I am currently a Master's Candidate at the University of Missouri
participating in the computer science 5 year Fast-Track Program to obtain
a Master of Science and Bachelor of Science in Computer Science along with a
minor in business. I earned my Bachelor of Science in Computer Science in
May of 2017 and expect to graduate with my Master of Science in May of 2018.
I am a motivated problem-solver striving to advance myself and gain a greater
understanding of the field of computer science through work with an innovative,
productive organization on the forefront of the field of computer science.
